    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Nos vir gloriosissimus
                            <persName key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma #Princeps"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/186">Sichardus</persName> Dei
                        providentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, motus
                        omnipotentis misericordia, pro redemptione anime nostrae seu gentis et
                        patriae, concedimus in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/84" key="#Monasteries #Abbots">Beatissimi
                            Benedicti</orgName> quo situm est in <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/109" key="#Castle #Monasteries">Casino</placeName>,
                        ubi <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/187"
                            >Authpert</persName> reverentissimus <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        regimen tenere videtur, <rs key="#Gualdi">vvaldum</rs> sacri nostri Palatii
                        qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Sea #Quarries #Gualdi #Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Martoranum</placeName>, qui habet fines de uno capite fine <rs
                            key="#Sea">mare</rs>, abinde fine foce de Betrana, deinde fine
                            <placeName key="#Villages/settlements">Bena de Putiu</placeName> et inde
                        in terra Montonata et inde <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/251" key="#Villages/settlements"
                            >Bena de Cosa</placeName> et fine cunione qui dicitur de Ippoli, has
                        fines discernit istum gualdum a <rs key="#Gualdi">gualdo</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Gualdi #Churches"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/121">Sancti Martini de
                            Prata</orgName>, et inde fine <rs key="#Quarries">arenarii </rs>et fine
                        termite qui dicitur <placeName key="#Villages/settlements"
                            >Ferola</placeName> et fine <placeName key="#Villages/settlements">Bena
                            de Carpinu</placeName> et fine signaida de cesa quae dicitur Mauri et
                        inde in cerque signate que dicitur Caedarolu et Benactola de Ficulcia quae
                        est inter hunc vvaldum et fine de<placeName key="#Villages/settlements">
                            Puranetu</placeName> et fine <rs key="#Rivers">flumine qui dicitur
                            Fertore</rs>, reconiungentes se in predicto mare, cum <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >ripis</rs> et aquis et <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >fussariis</rs> et <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs> et omnibus
                        infra positis, sicut actenus ad manus Palatii nostri pertinuit, pertinet
                            de<geogName key="#Rivers #Sea #Gualdi #Fisheries #Marepahis"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/140"> mari passato</geogName>
                        <persName key="#Marepahis">Arichis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marepahis">maripachis</rs> nostri, in ea videlicet ratione ut
                        amodo de deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum supradictum vvaldum per
                        designatos fines ipsum monasterium et eius rectores securo nomine habere et
                        possidere seu perfrui valeant, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, gastaldeis
                        vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeant aliquam requisitionem rectores predicti
                        monasterii ex prefato vvaldo, sed perpetuis temporibus in integrum
                        possideantur. Quod vero <rs key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">preceptum
                            concessionis</rs> ex iussione suprascripte potestatis scripsi ego
                            <persName key="#Notary">Audoaldus</persName><rs key="#Notary">
                            notarius</rs>. <date>Actu <placeName ref="#places/110" key="#Palatium"
                                >Benevento</placeName> in sacro <rs key="#Palatium">Palatio</rs>
                            quinto anno, mense Iunio, quintadecima indictione</date>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
